These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, doctor, dancer, analyst
1. the videographer is on the far left##1
2. the doctor is on the left or right of the videographer##3
3. the doctor is on the left or right of the dancer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Job   | videographer | doctor | dancer | analyst |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, sailing, biathlon, climbing
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | sailing | weightlifting | climbing | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, snowboarding, rugby
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | snowboarding | golf | rugby |

