.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, tulip, bellflower, orchid
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Flower   | tulip | balloon-flower | orchid | bellflower |

