.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, adventure, musical
1. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | adventure | romance | epic |

