3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Beverage   | cola | lemonade | 7up | hot-chocolate |

