2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |   3   |   4    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | hamster | goldfish | rat |

