2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| City   | hamburg | rome | boston | hannover |

