.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, motorbike, car
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the car##2
3. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Transport   | car | bike | roller | motorbike |

