.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, july, december
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2     |    3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | july | february | april | december |

