.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, blood-red, chestnut, lavender
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Color   | chestnut | blood-red | light-blue | lavender |

 